cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.IR, cs.AI, cs.CV

This paper deals with text classification using deep learning techniques, which falls under the sub-categories of natural language processing (cs.CL), machine learning (cs.LG), information retrieval (cs.IR), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), and computer vision (cs.CV). However, since the paper focuses on text classification, cs.CL is the most likely sub-category, followed by cs.LG and cs.IR. The use of deep learning techniques also makes cs.AI a likely sub-category, while the potential application of the proposed approach to image classification makes cs.CV a possible sub-category as well.
